^*Issue 1.2	Tony J Ibbs, 10 June 1986\*
.BLANK
.LM +8
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter #1 - INTRO
.BR; Remove discussion of meanings of severities (now in chapter 3). Alter
pagination slightly.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter #2 - LSLINIT
.BR; Describe check performed by EXPAND that LSL__INIT has been called.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter #3 - ERRORS
.BR; Add explanation of how LSL programs should use message severities.
Correct description of message definition format ("_<" and "_>" now used
as delimiters). Correct extensions of files produced to match new practice.
Add LSL__ADDMSG, and improve layout of routine descriptions. Add an example
for MARK__POSN. Correct various typing errors.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter #4 - EXPC
.BR; Correct typing errors.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter #5 - EXPAND
.BR; Mention EXPAND's check that LSL__INIT has been called. Correct typing
errors.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter #7 - EXCEPTION
.BR; Correct description of LSL____BADINEQ and LSL____AMBINEQ to reflect
new common /INEQUAL/.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter #9 - NUMBERS
.BR; Correct informal descriptions of real numbers (form "a.b" was omitted).
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter 11 - FILENAME
.BR; Correct typing errors. EXPFLN now also returns LSL____NOFIELD,
LSL____FILNOLEN.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter 13 - FILE
.BR; Correct typing errors. FLRSTR has new argument ^*nchs\*.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter 14 - DCL
.BR; Correct typing errors - real*8 replaced by real_*8 where necessary.
Examples now call LSL__INIT, not TMRINI.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter 15 - COMMANDS
.BR; Add new routine LSL__CMDERR, new common /INEQUAL/.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter 18 - SYSTEM
.BR; TMRINI now called LSL__TMRINI. New common /EXIT__HANDLER/ used by
LSL__TMRINI.
.LM -8

