.TP 10;.P 0
^*Issue 1.6	Bill James, Tony J Ibbs, Tim Hartnall, 29 April 1987\*
.BLANK
.LM +8
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter #1 - INTRO
.BR; "Differences from VIOLIB/CMDLIB" is actually an appendix of this document,
not a separate document. Document that return codes from functions may be (and
often are) ignored in VAX Fortran.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter #2 - LSLINIT
.BR; LSL__INIT has new argument ^*tracing\*, and now calls LSL__DEBUG__TRACE.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter #3 - ERROR__DEFN
.BR; The .GENMSG_* files are no longer generated by NEWMESSAGE, and thus
the format of message definition lines is simplified.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter #4 - ERROR__RTNS
.BR; LSL__PUTMSG no longer checks LSL$DEBUG__TRACE itself. Document
LSL__DEBUG__TRACE. Add another example of the use of LSL__PUTMSG and
LSL__ADDMSG. Use ^*ok\* as the name of the return variable for all functions.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter #6 - EXPC
.BR; DEF__EXPMAX is now 255. New routine SAVE__EXPMAX.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter #7 - EXPAND
.BR; %S and %A now default to 255 characters.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter #8 - TXTC
.BR; DEF__TXTLIM is now 255. New routine SAVE__TXTLIM.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter 12 - FILENAME
.BR; Use ^*ok\* as the name of the return variable for all functions.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter 13 - TERMINAL
.BR; Use ^*ok\* as the name of the return variable for all functions.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter 14 - FILE
.BR; New routines FLRSVL and FLWSVL save the current file selection.
.BR; Improve the documentation of the file open and file select routines.
.BR; Use ^*ok\* as the name of the return variable for all functions.
.BR; New routine FLWUSH flushes internal buffers to disc.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter 15 - DCL
.BR; Use ^*ok\* as the name of the return variable for all functions.
.BR; New routines START__LOG and START_LCM added for creation of Laser-Scan
utility /OUTPUT listing file and /LITES2 command file. 
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter 16 - COMMANDS
.BR; Use ^*ok\* as the name of the return variable for LSL__CMDERR.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter 17 - IFF
.BR; Improve the introduction to this chapter - mention the fact that the
LSL____IFFxxx error messages often require arguments.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter 18 - MAPPED
.BR; These routines are now all fully implemented. Document new arguments
to VIO$OPEN__SEC, and improve its description. Document VIO$UPDATE__SEC.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter 19 - MAGTAPE
.BR; Use ^*ok\* as the name of the return variable for LSL__CMDERR.
.TP3;.I-8; Chapter 20 - SYSTEM
.BR;New routine TRNALL added - does logical name translation.
.BR;New routine SET__OUTBAND__AST added.
.TP3;.I-8; Appendix B - COMPARISON
.BR; Update the comparison of current LSLLIB with VIOLIB/CMDLIB.
.LM -8


